once an archaic society, farmers have raised crops which have given way to a new form of revenue that has brought you prosperity, in turn,it strengthened the culture for the natives.

once an archaic society, they opened a drive in movie theater and bowling alley that has brought me happiness, and gold is no longer needed as currency.
once an archaic society, they opened a drive in movie theater and bowling alley that has brought me , and gold is no longer needed as currency.

although this area isn't the best, farmers have raised crops which have given way to a new form of revenue that has brought me new freedoms, in turn,it strengthened the culture for the natives.
although this area isn't the best, farmers have raised crops which have given way to a new form of revenue that has brought me , in turn,it strengthened the culture for the natives.

busy with massive summer tourism, they opened a drive in movie theater and bowling alley that has brought its citizens county fairs, and the previous ways they lived are now gone forever.
busy with massive summer tourism, they opened a drive in movie theater and bowling alley that has brought its citizens , and the previous ways they lived are now gone forever.
contradiction
